{"tid":704062,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性討論）考棍波心態","createTime":"2018-06-16T06:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T03:44:53.000Z","uid":126621,"like":11,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8e67eb9c3cadfdc06ee9d66d11b29e9fe6313192","tid":704062,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"如果考棍波比自動波貴1000~2000<br />\n起馬有八成人唔會考棍<br />\n根本係香港人貪小便宜心態<br />\n覺得同等價錢考多樣實好d<br />\n但無諗過自身問題<br />\n自己手腳協唔協調 有無需要呢d<br />\n唔配合自身需要去考棍根本反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 2次或以上先pass 既人無資格<br />\n笑1take pass自動波<br />\n<br />\n自動波容易d pass 我諗應該無人反對啦呱？<br />\n如果自己無需要揸棍波 做乜要同錢作對？<br />\n大部分人根本無需要棍波牌<br />\n如果你話外國自駕遊/揸van 搵食<br />\n呢d 就叫所謂既需要<br />\n<br />\n2.棍波係男人浪漫<br />\n<br />\n邊度浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n貪佢夠chok 溝到女？<br />\n你話棍波電單車浪漫<br />\n自動波羊唔浪漫 我就明<br />\n現實係有車就浪漫溝死女架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日見d 人拎棍波牌揸自動波車<br />\n跟住瘋狂打飛機 好想恥笑佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb199b44fe9e5d6c9d20fdf56714aba8c81b671","tid":704062,"uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:02:17.000Z","msg":"成日覺得自己唔同d 醒d<br />\n同等價錢實考多樣野好d<br />\n<br />\n到最後fail 左真係好柒<br />\n要考兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48062366e96395b31393143f8d570229015cd25","tid":704062,"uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":18,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"駁唔到就負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n考車好講運氣<br />\n就算一take pass 棍<br />\n可能只係你好彩<br />\n根本唔值得打飛機同自豪<br />\n咁只係會顯得你自大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3b30c15f63d01617b1cf0adb7a38b15eb920ed","tid":704062,"uid":121517,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"睇來樓豬眼紅人地考到棍波而自卑自己只是考到自動波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b654919b36daded6146bc118b568973e9be7690","tid":704062,"uid":14073,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"十年前考棍ok<br />\n今日真係無必要"},{"pid":"5392520be76f9ff2b10a1ab2f25fbfe7a9e4917d","tid":704062,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"4c3b30c15f63d01617b1cf0adb7a38b15eb920ed","tid":704062,"uid":121517,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"睇來樓豬眼紅人地考到棍波而自卑自己只是考到自動波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"我有棍波電單車牌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5115b08c3770e2f9b1e0f7d73ae04e15df22dadc","tid":704062,"uid":12662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"樓主手腳協調嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318e576578c9d3aad14e78042d6ea0f2184b6338","tid":704062,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5115b08c3770e2f9b1e0f7d73ae04e15df22dadc","tid":704062,"uid":12662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"樓主手腳協調嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}